snippet.title: (NO EAS) Corpus Christi, TX - Texas AMBER Alert - 06/08/2021
snippet.description:
This is a typical event in Texas.

https://mesonet.agron.iastate.edu/wx/afos/p.php?pil=CAEFWD&e=202106090314

BULLETIN - EAS ACTIVATION REQUESTED
CHILD ABDUCTION EMERGENCY
TEXAS DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY
RELAYED BY NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE FORT WORTH TX
1014 PM CDT TUE JUN 8 2021

THE FOLLOWING MESSAGE IS TRANSMITTED AT THE REQUEST OF THE TEXAS
DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY.

THIS IS A CHILD ABDUCTION ALERT ISSUED BY THE TEXAS AMBER ALERT 
NETWORK

THE CORPUS CHRISTI POLICE DEPARTMENT IS SEARCHING FOR ZAYLEE
ZAMORA, WHITE, FEMALE, 1 YEAR OLD, 2 FEET 2 INCHES, 25 POUNDS, 
BLACK HAIR, BROWN EYES, AND LAST SEEN WEARING UNKNOWN CLOTHING. 
VICTIM HAS RIGHT EAR PIERCED ONLY AND RIGHT INDEX FINGER HAS 
BRUISING.

POLICE ARE LOOKING FOR KRISTIAN ARIEL GARCIA, WHITE, MALE,
24 YEARS OLD, 5 FEET 7 INCHES, 160 POUNDS, BLACK HAIR, BROWN EYES
AND LAST SEEN WEARING A WHITE HOODIE WITH A BLACK MASK, IN 
CONNECTION WITH HER ABDUCTION.

THE SUSPECT WAS LAST HEARD FROM IN CORPUS CHRISTI, TEXAS.

LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICIALS BELIEVE THIS CHILD TO BE IN GRAVE OR
IMMEDIATE DANGER.

IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION REGARDING THIS ABDUCTION, CALL THE
CORPUS CHRISTI POLICE DEPARTMENT AT 
3...6...1...8...8...6...2...6...0... 0

NEWS MEDIA POINT OF CONTACT IS CORPUS CHRISTI POLICE DEPARTMENT
AT
3...6...1...8...8...6...2...7...9...8. END OF MESSAGE.
